1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: Andrija and Andjelka face difficulties while shopping,have problems in bed and have an eventful dinner at the restaurant.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: Andrija and Andjelka argue in the car,go shopping and have dinner with friends.

3.title: Episode #1.3
3.plot: Andjelka and Andrija argue about going to her mother for dinner.At dinner Andrija and her mother show their hatred towards one another. Andrija and Andjelka have amusing moments at the cinema.

4.title: Episode #1.4
4.plot: Andjelka decides they need to go to the psychiatrist. Andrija suggests places for their vacation but Andjelka rejects every destination. After their vacation they have dinner at theirs friends house to give them souvenirs.

5.title: Episode #1.5
5.plot: Andrija and Andjelka decide to go to a gym but Andjelka breaks her leg during exercise.

imdb.plot outline: Andrija i Andjelka , a couple in their mid thirties, are a typical example of what happens when a man and woman live together. Although they sincerely love each other, they often get on each others nerves, whether in the bedroom, at supermarket or at dinner with friends.
imdb.title: Andrija i Andjelka
plot: _Andrija i Andjelka_ (qv) , a couple in their mid thirties, are a typical example of what happens when a man and woman live together. Although they sincerely love each other, they often get on each others nerves, whether in the bedroom, at supermarket or at dinner with friends.
